'''Candace Warner''' is a fourth-year medical student who did a [[Clerkship|rotation]] at [[Grey Sloan Memorial Hospital]].

==History==
Candace came to the hospital to work as a [[Clerkship|sub-intern]]. On her first day, while she was on a tour, she annoyed Richard by using the voice-to-notes app on her phone to record the tour and later, she screamed after seeing [[April Kepner]] do a thoracotomy in the ER. ''("[[Break Down the House]]")''

After the sub-interns were challenged to find [[Megan Hunt]] a suitable abdominal wall donor, Candace suggested a male patient. ''("[[Get Off on the Pain]]")''

==Career==
Candace is a fourth-year medical student doing a six-week rotation as a [[Clerkship|sub-intern]] at Grey Sloan Memorial.

==Notes and Trivia==
*Candace is in the top 10% of her medical school program.
*Candace prefers to dictate notes into her phone.
